{"id":149588,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/简讯：中国称拉登之死是积极进展/","date":"2011-05-03T16:30:23Z","modified":"2011-05-03T16:30:23Z","title":"简讯：中国称拉登之死是积极进展","content":"<div>\n<p>“基地”组织领导人本·拉登在巴基斯坦被美军击毙，中国外交部发言人姜瑜周一（2日）就此表示，这是国际反恐斗争的重要事件和积极进展。</p>\n<p>她说，恐怖主义是国际社会公敌。中国也是恐怖主义的受害者。中国历来反对一切形式的恐怖主义，并积极参与国际反恐斗争。</p>\n<p>姜瑜还表示，反恐应标本兼治，努力消除恐怖主义滋生的土壤。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>\t<a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/china/2011/05/#page-top\" rel=\"nofollow\"><br />\n\t\t<span>点击</span><br />\n\t\t<span>页首</span><br />\n\t</a></div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/iLpKjPGchfvWm7DtEJnKDYHLbw4/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/iLpKjPGchfvWm7DtEJnKDYHLbw4/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/iLpKjPGchfvWm7DtEJnKDYHLbw4/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/iLpKjPGchfvWm7DtEJnKDYHLbw4/1/di\"></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/s5Jzd_QioZ8\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[15571]}